## inline config

`linthtml-enable, linthtml-disable, linthtml-configure` cannot be use to activate new rules
only affect configured rules (already defined before)

<div>
  <div>
    foo // not ignored
    {{!-- linthtml-disable rule=config --}}
    <div>
      foo // ignored
    </div>
    foo // ignored
  </div>
  foo // not ignored
</div>
